description: BBQ Revolution is a food truck dedicated to bringing people the best possible vegan foods in the best city to be vegan: Austin, Texas! Menu items include Vegan "Brisket" made from Wheat Roast, Garbanzo Tempeh "Ribs," and soy curls. Sides include "mom's" Potato Salad, Coleslaw, Beans, and a special rotating Mac and Cheese. BBQ Revolution uses as many local vendors and ingredients as possible, and actually smokes all proteins on a true smoker! If you believe that BBQ doesn't have to equal meat, head over and join the revolution!
name: BBQ Revolution
